.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: parkour, biathlon, water-polo, skiing, lacrosse, climbing, volleyball
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, quad-bike, train, snowmobile, car, jet-ski, subway
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person driving the car is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the subway and the person who's sport is skiing##2
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Sport   | volleyball | lacrosse | parkour | biathlon   | skiing | water-polo | climbing |
| Transport           | car | jet-ski     | quad-bike     | train | snowmobile   | taxi   | subway    |

