.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, bus, car, subway, jet-ski, roller, ship
The people have 7 different hobbies: reading, gardening, woodworking, drawing, traveling, sudoku, collecting
 1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person driving the car and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
 7. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 9. the person driving the bus is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Transport      | car    | jet-ski  | subway  | bike  | ship      | roller       | bus |
| Hobby   | traveling | drawing | sudoku | collecting | reading | woodworking | gardening  |

