.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, tea, lemonade, 7up, iced-tea, soy-milk, sprite
7 different pets are kept: dog, chinchilla, bird, hamster, snake, ferret, pony
1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the snake is the person drinking tea##1
3. the owner of the dog is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking water##2
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person drinking water##1
7. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
8. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking 7up##1
9. the person drinking iced-tea is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Beverage   | 7up      | iced-tea | water | lemonade | sprite      | tea      | soy-milk |
| Pet     | chinchilla | ferret | pony       | dog | bird | snake | hamster |

