3. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating kale##1
4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
6. the person eating blueberry is between the person eating onion and the fonseca-smoker##2
7. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
8. the dunhill-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
