.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
7 different pets are kept: rat, rabbit, pony, horse, dog, mouse, bird
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, malaysian, brazilian, egyptian, japanese, argentine, french
 1. the argentine is the owner of the dog##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the french##1
 3. the malaysian is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the pony is between the japanese and the french##2
 5. the pakistani is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 6. the owner of the rat is on the left of the pakistani##1
 7. the egyptian is the owner of the rat##1
 8. the owner of the mouse is the japanese##1
 9. the brazilian is between the japanese and the owner of the dog##2
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Pet   | rat | rabbit    | horse | pony   | mouse | bird    | dog |
| Nationality      | egyptian | pakistani | french    | malaysian | japanese    | brazilian | argentine  |

