 1. the fan country is on the left of the fan pop##1
 2. the fan r&b is on the left of the fan soul##1
 3. the fan trance is on the far left##1
 4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 5. the fan country is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the goat##2
 7. the fan hip-hop is on the right of the fan trance##1
 8. the fan r&b is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 9. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
10. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the cat##2
11. the fan country is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Pet   | turtle  | hamster   | cat         | horse     | goat              | guinea-pig    | ferret     |
| Music-Genre        | trance | hip-hop | country | pop | ambient | r&b | soul |

